message.content:
I have created a CSV file containing information about the first five Presidents of the United States. Here is the content of the CSV file:

```
Name,Age When Started Office,Year Started Office,Number of Years Served
George Washington,57,1789,2
John Adams,61,1797,1
Thomas Jefferson,57,1801,3
James Madison,57,1809,5
James Monroe,58,1817,4
```

Please note that the ages are approximate as they were calculated based on their birth years and the year they started office.
